#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Usually program messages and documentation are written in English. Using a "
"framework made of a set of tools and libraries, it is possible to have your "
"favorite applications speak your native non-English language. This process "
"of adapting an application to a specific language is known as "
"<emphasis>localization</emphasis>. The localization process includes "
"translating the program's interfaces and documentation to the various "
"languages users need and, in some countries or regions, making the inputs "
"and outputs conform to particular conventions. &lokalize; is a tool which "
"will assist you in the localization process to make an application's "
"interface speaks many languages."
msgstr ""
"Običajno so programska sporočila in dokumentacija napisana v angleščini. Z "
"uporabo ogrodja, sestavljenega iz nabora orodij in knjižnic, je možno, da "
"vaše najljubše aplikacije govorijo vaš materni neangleški jezik. Ta postopek "
"prilagajanja aplikacije določenemu jeziku je znan kot "
"<emphasis>lokalizacija</emphasis>. Postopek lokalizacije vključuje "
"prevajanje programskih vmesnikov in dokumentacije v različne jezike, ki jih "
"potrebujejo uporabniki, in v nekaterih državah ali regijah prilagajanje "
"vhodnih in izhodnih podatkov določenim konvencijam. &lokalize; je orodje, ki "
"vam bo pomagalo pri procesu lokalizacije, da bo vmesnik aplikacije govoril "
"več jezikov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:62
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Every internationalization-aware program makes available for translation one "
"or more message-catalog files. The extension of these files is <filename "
"class=\"extension\">.pot</filename>. <acronym>POT</acronym> is an acronym "
"for <quote>Portable Object Template</quote>. &lokalize; is an advanced and "
"easy to use PO file (&GNU; gettext message catalogs) editor. It is a "
"computer-aided translation system for translators, written from scratch "
"using the &kde; Platform 4 framework. Aside from basic editing of PO files "
"with nifty auxiliary details, it integrates support for glossary, "
"translation memory, diff-modes for QA, project managing, &etc; It has many "
"features like full navigation capabilities, extensive editing functionality, "
"search functions, syntax checking and statistics functions."
msgstr ""
"Vsak program, ki se zaveda internacionalizacije da na voljo za prevod eno "
"ali več datotek kataloga sporočil. Končnica teh datotek je <filename class="
"\"extension\">.pot</filename>. <acronym>POT</acronym> je akronim za "
"<quote>Predloga prenosnega predmeta</quote>. &lokalize; je napreden in "
"enostaven urejevalnik datotek PO (&GNU; gettext message catalogs). Je "
"računalniško podprt prevajalski sistem za prevajalce, napisan iz nič z "
"uporabo &kde; Okvir platforme 4. Poleg osnovnega urejanja datotek PO z "
"izvrstnimi pomožnimi podrobnostmi vključuje podporo za glosar, pomnilnik "
"prevodov, diff-načine za QA, vodenje projektov itd. Ima številne funkcije, "
"kot so popolne navigacijske zmogljivosti, obsežna funkcionalnost urejanja, "
"funkcije iskanja, preverjanje sintakse in statistične funkcije."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:65
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Portable Object (.po) files: Each translator takes a copy of one of these "
"POT templates and begins to fill in the blanks: each message is translated "
"into the language desired. The file containing the translated text is "
"referred to as a PO (Portable Object) file."
msgstr ""
"Datoteke Portable Object (.po): Vsak prevajalec vzame kopijo ene od teh "
"predlog POT in začne izpolnjevati praznine: vsako sporočilo je prevedeno v "
"želeni jezik. Datoteka, ki vsebuje prevedeno besedilo, se imenuje datoteka "
"PO (Portable Object)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid "Editor"
msgstr "Urejevalnik"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid "Main Window"
msgstr "Glavno okno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default, the main window contains six parts. The upper-right box is read-"
"only and contains the current msgid (source text) field from the opened PO-"
"file. The edit box just below this contains the msgstr (target text) field "
"related to the msgid shown and here you can input or edit the translated "
"text."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto glavno okno vsebuje šest delov. Zgornje desno polje je samo za "
"branje in vsebuje trenutno polje msgid (izvorno besedilo) iz odprte datoteke "
"PO. Polje za urejanje tik pod tem vsebuje polje msgstr (ciljno besedilo), "
"povezano s prikazanim sporočilom msgid, in tukaj lahko vnesete ali uredite "
"prevedeno besedilo."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid "The main default &lokalize; window"
msgstr "Glavno privzeto &lokalize; okno"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid "This shows the default window when a file is opened."
msgstr "To prikaže privzeto okno, ko je datoteka odprta."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The top-left part of the main window shows the Translation Units. Below "
"this, there is Unit Metadata section and it contains comments relevant to "
"the currently displayed source text. In the lower-left, there is a "
"Translation Memory section which shows the suggested translations from the "
"translation memory database for the current source text entry. On the lower-"
"right corner of the window, the glossary section is shown."
msgstr ""
"Zgornji levi del glavnega okna prikazuje prevajalske enote. Pod tem je "
"razdelek Metapodatki enote, ki vsebuje komentarje, ki so pomembni za "
"trenutno prikazano izvorno besedilo. V spodnjem levem kotu je razdelek "
"Prevajalski pomnilnik, ki prikazuje predlagane prevode iz zbirke podatkov "
"prevajalskega pomnilnika za trenutni vnos izvornega besedila. V spodnjem "
"desnem kotu okna je prikazan del glosarja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Translation files are opened in separate tabs, with two big multi-line edits "
"as well as a bunch of <emphasis>tool views</emphasis>. These views can be "
"stacked (similar to tabs), shown separately, or hidden. Translation files "
"consist of many English-target pairs called <emphasis>units</emphasis>. A "
"<emphasis>unit</emphasis> typically correspond to a single string in the "
"user interface, or one paragraph in the documentation. The purpose of the "
"first multi-line edit is to display the original part of the pair. The "
"purpose of the second multi-line edit is to display the translation. You can "
"navigate through the <emphasis>units</emphasis> via the "
"<guilabel>Translation Units</guilabel> view or by using <keycap>Page Down</"
"keycap> and <keycap>Page Up</keycap>."
msgstr ""
"Datoteke s prevodi se odprejo v ločenih zavihkih, z dvema velikima "
"urejanjema v več vrsticah in množico <emphasis>pogledov orodij</emphasis>. "
"Ti pogledi so lahko zloženi (podobno kot zavihki), prikazani ločeno ali "
"skriti. Prevajalske datoteke so sestavljene iz številnih ciljnih parov v "
"angleščini, imenovanih <emphasis>enote</emphasis>. <emphasis>Enota</"
"emphasis> običajno ustreza enemu nizu v uporabniškem vmesniku ali enemu "
"odstavku v dokumentaciji. Namen prvega večvrstičnega urejanja je prikazati "
"izvirni del para. Namen drugega večvrstičnega urejanja je prikazati prevod. "
"Po <emphasis>enotah</emphasis> se lahko pomikate prek pogleda "
"<guilabel>Prevajalske enote</guilabel> ali z uporabo <keycap>Page Down</"
"keycap> in <keycap>Page Up</keycap>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A unit may be <emphasis>translated</emphasis> or <emphasis>untranslated</"
"emphasis>. A translation of a translated unit may be <emphasis>ready</"
"emphasis> or <emphasis>not ready</emphasis> (also called <emphasis>fuzzy</"
"emphasis> sometimes). If the unit is not ready, its translation is rendered "
"in italics. &lokalize; allows you to easily navigate through the file "
"according to the state of their translation. See <guilabel>Go</guilabel> "
"menu for the shortcuts. The status bar at the bottom of the window shows the "
"current string number, total number of strings, total untranslated strings, "
"total not ready (fuzzy) strings and status of the current string "
"respectively. When navigating, untranslated units are treated as not ready. "
"Also, you may use the filtering feature of <guilabel>Translation Units</"
"guilabel> toolview. Pressing <keycap>Page Down</keycap> actually takes you "
"to the next unit in filtered/sorted list of that tool view."
msgstr ""
"Enota je lahko <emphasis>prevedena</emphasis> ali <emphasis>neprevedena</"
"emphasis>. Prevod prevedene enote je lahko <emphasis>pripravljen</emphasis> "
"ali <emphasis>ni pripravljen</emphasis> (včasih imenovan tudi "
"<emphasis>nejasen</emphasis>). Če enota ni pripravljena, je njen prevod "
"upodobljen v poševnem tisku. &lokalize; vam omogoča preprosto krmarjenje po "
"datoteki glede na stanje njihovega prevoda. Glejte meni <guilabel>Pojdi</"
"guilabel> za bližnjice. Vrstica stanja na dnu okna prikazuje trenutno "
"številko niza, skupno število nizov, skupno število neprevedenih nizov, "
"skupno število nepripravljenih (mehkih) nizov in stanje trenutnega niza. Med "
"krmarjenjem se neprevedene enote obravnavajo kot nepripravljene. Uporabite "
"lahko tudi funkcijo filtriranja orodja <guilabel>Enote prevajanja</"
"guilabel>. S pritiskom <keycap>Page Down</keycap> se dejansko pomaknete na "
"naslednjo enoto na filtriranem/razvrščenem seznamu tega pogleda orodja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To ease up translation of the console applications where spacers in messages "
"are important you can check the <guilabel>Visualize separators such as "
"spaces, tabs and new lines in the editor</guilabel> item on the page "
"<guilabel>Editing</guilabel> of the configuration window which can be opened "
"by choosing the <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure &lokalize;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> main "
"menu item."
msgstr ""
"Za olajšanje prevajanja konzolnih aplikacij, kjer so presledki v sporočilih "
"pomembni, lahko preverite element <guilabel>Vizualiziraj ločila, kot so "
"presledki, zavihki in nove vrstice v urejevalniku</guilabel> na strani "
"<guilabel>Urejanje</guilabel> konfiguracijskega okna, ki ga lahko odprete "
"tako, da izberete element glavnega menija <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj &lokalize;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have no access to the original translation template file (it is a "
"common practice on some commercial translation projects) then you can use a "
"translation file from the related language. Just choose the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Clear all translated "
"entries</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item or use <keycombo>&Ctrl;&Alt;"
"<keycap>D</keycap></keycombo> shortcut to clear all translation units."
msgstr ""
"Če nimate dostopa do izvirne datoteke predloge prevoda (to je običajna "
"praksa pri nekaterih komercialnih prevajalskih projektih), potem lahko "
"uporabite datoteko prevoda iz sorodnega jezika. Preprosto izberite menijski "
"element <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Počisti vse "
"prevedene vnose</guimenuitem></menuchoice> ali uporabite <keycombo>&Ctrl;"
"&Alt;<keycap>D</keycap></keycombo> bližnjica za brisanje vseh prevajalskih "
"enot."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:117
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To the main window one can add many more sections like <guilabel>Alternate "
"Translations</guilabel>, <guilabel>Primary Sync</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Secondary Sync</guilabel>, <guilabel>Binary Units</guilabel> by "
"using <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Toolviews</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> from the main menu."
msgstr ""
"V glavno okno lahko dodate veliko več razdelkov, kot so <guilabel>Nadomestni "
"prevodi</guilabel>, <guilabel>Primarna sinhronizacija</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Sekundarna sinhronizacija</guilabel>, <guilabel>Binarne enote</"
"guilabel> z uporabo <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Pogledi orodij</guimenuitem></menuchoice> iz glavnega "
"menija."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid "Toolbars"
msgstr "Orodne vrstice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:124
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can add or remove actions in the toolbars using "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Toolbars...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> from the main menu."
msgstr ""
"Dejanja v orodnih vrsticah lahko dodate ali odstranite z "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj orodne "
"vrstice...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> v glavnem meniju."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:128
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configure Toolbars"
msgstr "Konfigurirajte orodne vrstice"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here you can configure the toolbars."
msgstr "Tukaj lahko konfigurirate orodne vrstice."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:138
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information read the section about <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/"
"config.html#toolbars\">Toolbars</ulink> of the &kde; Fundamentals."
msgstr ""
"Za več informacij preberite razdelek o <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/"
"config.html#toolbars\">Orodnih vrsticah</ulink> v &kde; Osnove."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:142
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shortcut keys"
msgstr "Bližnjične tipke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:143
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can save time by using shortcut keys during translation. To configure "
"shortcut keys, use <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Shortcuts...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> from "
"the main menu."
msgstr ""
"Z uporabo bližnjičnih tipk med prevajanjem lahko prihranite čas. Za "
"konfiguracijo tipk za bližnjice uporabite <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj bližnjic...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> v "
"glavnem meniju."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configure Shortcuts"
msgstr "Konfigurirajte bližnjice"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:153
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here you can configure the shortcut keys."
msgstr "Tukaj lahko konfigurirate bližnjične tipke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:157
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information read the section about <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/"
"config.html#shortcuts\">Shortcuts</ulink> of the &kde; Fundamentals."
msgstr ""
"Za več informacij preberite razdelek o <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/"
"config.html#shortcuts\">Bližnjicah</ulink> v &kde; Osnove."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:161
#, no-c-format
msgid "General Tips"
msgstr "Splošni nasveti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are doing translations for &kde;, then either you will already have "
"&lokalize; project file in your language folder (usually named "
"<filename>index.lokalize</filename>), or you can select "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Project</guimenu><guimenuitem>Create new project</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> and the wizard will download translation files for "
"your language and will create project for you."
msgstr ""
"Če delate prevode za &kde;, boste bodisi že imeli &lokalize; projektno "
"datoteko v vaši jezikovni mapi (običajno imenovana <filename>index.lokalize</"
"filename>), lahko pa izberete <menuchoice><guimenu>Projekt</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Ustvari nov projekt</guimenuitem></menuchoice> in "
"čarovnik bo prenesel prevodne datoteke za vaš jezik in ustvaril projekt za "
"vas."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:169
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is recommended that you get used to the keyboard shortcuts instead of the "
"menus and toolbars for increased productivity. For example, use the "
"<keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>L</keycap></keycombo> to focus <guilabel>Quick "
"search</guilabel> input line to filter the unit list in "
"<guilabel>Translation Units</guilabel> view. Once you are done, press "
"<keycap>Page Down</keycap> to start moving along the filtered list. Pressing "
"<keycap>Esc</keycap> in the filter input will move the focus back to the "
"target text field without selecting another unit."
msgstr ""
"Priporočljivo je, da se za večjo produktivnost namesto menijev in orodnih "
"vrstic navadite na bližnjice na tipkovnici. Na primer, za filtriranje "
"seznama enot v pogledu <guilabel>Prevodne enote</guilabel> uporabite "
"<keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>L</keycap></keycombo>. Ko končate, pritisnite "
"<keycap>PageDown</keycap>, da se začnete premikati po filtriranem seznamu. "
"Če v vnosnem polju filtra pritisnete <keycap>Esc</keycap>, se fokus premakne "
"nazaj na ciljno besedilno polje, ne da bi izbrali drugo enoto."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:179
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are working with translation files in XLIFF format (definitely the "
"case when you translate OpenDocument), then extended states are available "
"(<emphasis>new</emphasis>, <emphasis>needs review</emphasis>, "
"<emphasis>approved</emphasis>, &etc;). You may select them in drop-down menu "
"of <guilabel>Approved</guilabel> button in the toolbar. Classification of "
"the state as <emphasis>ready</emphasis> or <emphasis>not ready</emphasis> "
"depends on the current <emphasis>workflow phase</emphasis> "
"(<emphasis>translation</emphasis>, <emphasis>review</emphasis>, "
"<emphasis>approval</emphasis>). A default phase for you depends on your "
"<emphasis>role</emphasis> in the project (set in project settings). Each "
"unit usually contains information about phase it was changed last time, and "
"for each phase its owner is logged to the file."
msgstr ""
"Če delate s prevodnimi datotekami v formatu XLIFF (zagotovo tako, ko "
"prevajate OpenDocument), so na voljo razširjena stanja (<emphasis>novo</"
"emphasis>, <emphasis>potreben je pregled</emphasis>, <emphasis>odobreno</"
"emphasis> itd.). Izberete jih lahko v spustnem meniju gumba "
"<guilabel>Odobreno</guilabel> v orodni vrstici. Razvrstitev stanja kot "
"<emphasis>pripravljeno</emphasis> ali <emphasis>ni pripravljeno</emphasis> "
"je odvisno od trenutne <emphasis>faze poteka dela</emphasis> "
"(<emphasis>prevod</emphasis>, <emphasis>pregled </emphasis>, "
"<emphasis>odobritev</emphasis>). Privzeta faza za vas je odvisna od vaše "
"<emphasis>vloge</emphasis> v projektu (nastavljene v nastavitvah projekta). "
"Vsaka enota običajno vsebuje informacije o fazi, ko je bila nazadnje "
"spremenjena, in za vsako fazo je njen lastnik prijavljen v datoteko."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:193
#, no-c-format
msgid "Projects"
msgstr "Projekti"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:196
#, no-c-format
msgid "General Notes"
msgstr "Splošne opombe"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:197
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The projects are one of the main concepts in &lokalize;. A project is "
"represented by a file that contains paths, folders with translations, "
"templates, and other files: glossary file, automation scripts, translation "
"memories. Whenever &lokalize; opens a file without a project loaded, it will "
"search for a project file in the parent folders (up to four levels). "
"Alternatively, you can specify the project file via the <userinput>--"
"project</userinput> flag when starting &lokalize; from the command line."
msgstr ""
"Projekti so eden glavnih konceptov v &lokalize;. Projekt predstavlja "
"datoteka, ki vsebuje poti, mape s prevodi, predloge in druge datoteke: "
"datoteka glosarja, avtomatizacijski skripti, pomnilniki prevodov. Kadarkoli "
"&lokalize; odpre datoteko brez naloženega projekta, bo iskal projektno "
"datoteko v nadrejenih mapah (do štiri ravni). Druga možnost je, da podate "
"projektno datoteko prek zastavice <userinput>--project</userinput>, ko "
"zaženete &lokalize; iz ukazne vrstice."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:206
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For each project you select your role in it (<emphasis>translator</"
"emphasis>, <emphasis>reviewer</emphasis>, <emphasis>approver</emphasis>), "
"which in turn affects the workflow phase &lokalize; automatically picks up "
"for files you edit."
msgstr ""
"Za vsak projekt izberete svojo vlogo v njem (<emphasis>prevajalec</"
"emphasis>, <emphasis>ocenjevalec</emphasis>, <emphasis>odobrovalec</"
"emphasis>), kar posledično vpliva na fazo poteka dela katero &lokalize; "
"samodejno izbere za datoteke, ki jih urejate."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:211
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is possible to define a word wrapping position on a project level. Just "
"use the <menuchoice><guimenu>Project</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure "
"project...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item then go to the "
"<guilabel>Advanced</guilabel> page."
msgstr ""
"Možno je definirati položaj prelivanja besed na ravni projekta. Preprosto "
"uporabite menijsko postavko <menuchoice><guimenu>Projekt</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj projekt...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> in pojdite "
"na stran <guilabel>Napredno</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:216
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Translation memories (unlike project files, glossary and scripts) are not "
"shared between the translation team members, as they are created and stored "
"under the user's home folder, meaning that the translation memories for all "
"of the projects are stored in the same folder and thus can be used when "
"other projects are opened."
msgstr ""
"Prevajalski pomnilniki (za razliko od projektnih datotek, glosarja in "
"skriptov) niso v skupni rabi med člani prevajalske skupine, saj so "
"ustvarjeni in shranjeni v uporabnikovi domači mapi, kar pomeni, da so "
"prevodni pomnilniki za vse projekte shranjeni v isti mapi in tako se lahko "
"uporabi, ko se odprejo drugi projekti."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:226
#, no-c-format
msgid "Project Overview tab"
msgstr "Zavihek Pregled projekta"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:227
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you start &lokalize; first time, you will see an empty "
"<guilabel>Project Overview</guilabel> tab. Project Overview is a file "
"manager view, which helps you keep an overview of your PO files. The "
"&lokalize; suite will help you to translate quickly and also to keep "
"translations consistent. &lokalize; workflow implies that you start with "
"creating/opening a project."
msgstr ""
"Ko prvič zaženete &lokalize; boste videli prazen zavihek <guilabel>Pregled "
"projekta</guilabel>. Pregled projekta je pogled upravitelja datotek, ki vam "
"pomaga ohraniti pregled nad datotekami PO. &lokalize; zbirka vam bo pomagala "
"pri hitrem prevajanju in ohranjanju doslednosti prevodov. &lokalize; potek "
"dela pomeni, da začnete z ustvarjanjem/odpiranjem projekta."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:230
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To create a new project, use <menuchoice><guimenu>Project</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Create new project</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. This "
"will guide through the steps to create a new project. In <guimenu>Project</"
"guimenu> menu you can also find options like <guimenuitem>Project overview</"
"guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Configure project</guimenuitem>, "
"<guimenuitem>Open project</guimenuitem>, and <guimenuitem>Open recent "
"project</guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite ustvariti nov projekt, uporabite <menuchoice><guimenu>Projekt</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Ustvari nov projekt</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. To bo "
"vodilo skozi korake za ustvarjanje novega projekta. V meniju "
"<guimenu>Projekt</guimenu> lahko najdete tudi možnosti, kot so "
"<guimenuitem>Pregled projekta</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj "
"projekt</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Odpri projekt</guimenuitem> in "
"<guimenuitem> Odpri nedavni projekt</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:234
#, no-c-format
msgid "Project Overview Tab"
msgstr "Zavihek Pregled projekta"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:240
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here you can configure the project."
msgstr "Tukaj lahko konfigurirate projekt."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:245
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Project Overview</guilabel> tab displays a file tree with "
"statistics for a current project, such as the percentage of translated units "
"completed and the last translator. It allows you to open a selected file in "
"a new tab of the current &lokalize; window."
msgstr ""
"Zavihek <guilabel>Pregled projekta</guilabel> prikazuje drevo datotek s "
"statističnimi podatki za trenutni projekt, kot je odstotek dokončanih "
"prevedenih enot in zadnji prevajalec. Omogoča vam, da odprete izbrano "
"datoteko v novem zavihku trenutnega &lokalize; okna."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:252
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can switch off the completely translated files from the "
"<guilabel>Project Overview</guilabel> using the <guibutton>Hide completed "
"items</guibutton> button on the main toolbar or <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>T</"
"keycap></keycombo> default shortcut."
msgstr ""
"Popolnoma prevedene datoteke lahko izklopite iz <guilabel>Pregleda projekta</"
"guilabel> z uporabo gumba <guibutton>Skrij dokončane elemente</guibutton> v "
"glavni orodni vrstici ali z <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>T</keycap> </keycombo> "
"privzeto bližnjico."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:256
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you start &lokalize; the next time it will show the last opened file by "
"default. You can switch off this behavior with the <guilabel>Restore the "
"previously opened files when opening &lokalize;</guilabel> item on the page "
"<guilabel>General</guilabel> of the configuration window which can be opened "
"by choosing the <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure &lokalize;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> main "
"menu item. The same page can be used to configure &lokalize; behavior when "
"you switch to the next/previous tab in it. It is possible to go through the "
"tab list according to the tab positions or according to their activation "
"order."
msgstr ""
"Ko naslednjič zaženete &lokalize; bo privzeto prikazala zadnjo odprto "
"datoteko. To vedenje lahko izklopite z elementom <guilabel>Obnovi predhodno "
"odprte datoteke pri odpiranju &lokalize;a</guilabel> na strani "
"<guilabel>Splošno</guilabel> konfiguracijskega okna, ki ga lahko odprete z "
"izbiro <menuchoice> <guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj "
"&lokalize;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> element glavnega menija. Isto stran "
"lahko uporabite za konfiguracijo &lokalize; obnašanja, ko preklopite na "
"naslednji/prejšnji zavihek v njem. Po seznamu zavihkov se lahko premikate "
"glede na položaje zavihkov ali glede na njihov vrstni red aktivacije."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:264
#, no-c-format
msgid "Glossary"
msgstr "Slovar"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:266
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Have you ever become tired of typing the same long text sequence several "
"times just because it would take more time to find its translation for a "
"copy and paste? Now you will only have to find the (frequent) word sequence "
"in the <guilabel>Glossary</guilabel> view, and then insert it by pressing a "
"shortcut."
msgstr ""
"Ste se že kdaj naveličali večkratnega tipkanja istega dolgega besedilnega "
"zaporedja samo zato, ker bi trajalo več časa, da bi našli njegov prevod za "
"kopiranje in lepljenje? Zdaj boste morali poiskati samo (pogosto) zaporedje "
"besed v pogledu <guilabel>Glosar</guilabel> in ga nato vstaviti s pritiskom "
"na bližnjico."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:273
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Of course the glossary should be populated with word sequences first. "
"&lokalize; has a handy glossary editor that allows an explicit search over "
"the entire glossary."
msgstr ""
"Seveda je treba slovar najprej napolniti z zaporedji besed. &lokalize; ima "
"priročen urejevalnik slovara, ki omogoča izrecno iskanje po celotnem "
"glosarju."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:280
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>Glossary view in the bottom right corner displays glossary "
"entries appropriate for the current unit</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Pogled slovarja v spodnjem desnem kotu prikazuje vnose glosarja, "
"ki ustrezajo trenutni enoti</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:286
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>Glossary view in the bottom right corner displays glossary entries "
"appropriate for the current unit</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Pogled slovarja v spodnjem desnem kotu prikazuje vnose glosarja, ki "
"ustrezajo trenutni enoti</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:294
#, no-c-format
msgid "Translation Memory"
msgstr "Pomnilnik prevodov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:296
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Translation Memory</guilabel> view allows you to drag and drop "
"a folder with translation files from say &dolphin; into the view, and then, "
"within few minutes, translation suggestions will be shown automatically on "
"the unit switch. To insert the translation suggestions into the file, use "
"<keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>1</keycap></keycombo>, <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>2</"
"keycap></keycombo> and so on, depending on the number of suggestion."
msgstr ""
"Pogled <guilabel>Prevajalski pomnilnik</guilabel> vam omogoča, da povlečete "
"in spustite mapo s prevodnimi datotekami iz recimo &dolphin; v pogled, nato "
"pa se bodo v nekaj minutah na stikalu enote samodejno prikazali predlogi "
"prevodov. Za vstavljanje predlogov prevodov v datoteko uporabite "
"<keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>1</keycap></keycombo>, <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>2</"
"keycap></keycombo> in tako naprej, odvisno na število predlogov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:304
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Manage translation "
"memories</guimenuitem></menuchoice> to add/manage projects to your "
"Translation Memory. Here you can also import or export data from <filename "
"role=\"extension\">tmx</filename> file format."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite <menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Upravljanje "
"pomnilnikov prevodov</guimenuitem></menuchoice> za dodajanje/upravljanje "
"projektov v vaš pomnilnik prevodov. Tukaj lahko tudi uvozite ali izvozite "
"podatke iz zapisa datoteke <filename role=\"extension\">tmx</filename>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:308
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Pressing <keycombo><keycap>F7</keycap></keycombo> will open "
"<guilabel>Translation Memory</guilabel> tab, which allows you to query the "
"TM freely. Clicking a search result will open the corresponding file and "
"unit. If you want to quickly open some file in the project (and it is added "
"to TM), then instead of browsing <guilabel>Project Overview</guilabel> you "
"can just type its name into the <guilabel>File mask</guilabel> field, "
"accompanied by '*'."
msgstr ""
"Če pritisnete <keycombo><keycap>F7</keycap></keycombo>, se odpre zavihek "
"<guilabel>Prevajalski pomnilnik</guilabel>, ki vam omogoča prosto "
"poizvedovanje po TM. S klikom na rezultat iskanja se odpre ustrezna datoteka "
"in enota. Če želite hitro odpreti neko datoteko v projektu (in je dodana v "
"TM), lahko namesto brskanja po <guilabel>Pregled projekta</guilabel> "
"preprosto vnesete njeno ime v <guilabel>Masko datoteke</guilabel> polje, ki "
"ga spremlja '*'."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:315
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The TM engine indexes all entries, including non-ready and untranslated "
"ones. This allows it to completely replace the Search-in-Files feature which "
"required scanning every file in the project each time a search is done."
msgstr ""
"Mehanizem TM indeksira vse vnose, vključno z nepripravljenimi in "
"neprevedenimi. To mu omogoča, da popolnoma nadomesti funkcijo Iskanje v "
"datotekah, ki je zahtevala skeniranje vsake datoteke v projektu ob vsakem "
"iskanju."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:321
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The outdated TM entries will be deleted from the &lokalize; translation "
"memory on rescan or clicking a missing entry if you check the "
"<guilabel>Delete missing files from translation memory on Rescan or when "
"clicking a missing entry</guilabel> item on the page <guilabel>Translation "
"Memory</guilabel> of the configuration window which can be opened by "
"choosing the <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure "
"&lokalize;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> main menu item."
msgstr ""
"Zastareli vnosi TM bodo izbrisani iz &lokalize; pomnilnika prevodov ob "
"ponovnem skeniranju ali kliku manjkajočega vnosa, če označite element "
"<guilabel>Izbriši manjkajoče datoteke iz pomnilnika prevodov pri ponovnem "
"skeniranju ali ko kliknete manjkajoči vnos</guilabel> na strani "
"<guilabel>Pomnilnik prevodov</guilabel> konfiguracijskega okna, ki ga lahko "
"odprete z izbiro glavne menijske postavke <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj &lokalize;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:326
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>&lokalize; with translation memory search results for the "
"current unit</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>&lokalize; z rezultati iskanja po pomnilniku prevodov za "
"trenutno enoto</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:332
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>&lokalize; with translation memory search results for the current "
"unit</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>&lokalize; z rezultati iskanja po pomnilniku prevodov za trenutno "
"enoto</phrase>"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:339
#, no-c-format
msgid "Batch Translation:"
msgstr "Paketni prevod:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:341
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To insert the exactly matching suggestion automatically from the translation "
"memory database, use <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Fill "
"in all exact suggestions</guimenuitem></menuchoice> OR <guimenuitem>Fill in "
"all exact suggestions and mark as fuzzy</guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite samodejno vstaviti predlog, ki se natančno ujema, iz zbirke "
"podatkov pomnilnika prevodov, uporabite <menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Izpolni vse natančne predloge</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> ALI <guimenuitem>Izpolni vse natančne predloge in označi kot "
"mehko</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:351
#, no-c-format
msgid "Translation Synchronization Capabilities"
msgstr "Zmožnosti sinhronizacije prevodov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:353
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Sync Mode</guilabel> (previously known as <guilabel>Merge "
"Mode</guilabel>) saves a great deal of time for the editors, and for cases "
"when two or more translators are working simultaneously on the same file, or "
"when one has to maintain translations for several branches of software."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Način sinhronizacije</guilabel> (prej znan kot <guilabel>Način "
"spajanja</guilabel>) urednikom prihrani veliko časa in v primerih, ko dva "
"ali več prevajalcev hkrati dela na isti datoteki, ali ko je treba vzdrževati "
"prevode za več vej programske opreme."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:360
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&lokalize; allows quick navigation through units that differ, and displays "
"word-by-word differences. Also, &lokalize; has two Sync views - "
"<guilabel>Primary Sync</guilabel> and <guilabel>Secondary Sync</guilabel>. "
"They are identical, but the former is usually used to merge translations and "
"second to keep in sync translations for two software branches."
msgstr ""
"&lokalize; omogoča hitro navigacijo med enotami, ki se razlikujejo, in "
"prikazuje razlike med besedami. Prav tako ima &lokalize; dva pogleda "
"sinhronizacije - <guilabel>Primarna sinhronizacija</guilabel> in "
"<guilabel>Sekundarna sinhronizacija</guilabel>. Sta enaka, vendar se prvi "
"običajno uporablja za združevanje prevodov, drugi pa za sinhronizacijo "
"prevodov za dve programski veji."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:366
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After you copied translation from auxiliary file (<emphasis>synchronized</"
"emphasis> it), any subsequent changes made to this unit will be replicated "
"back to auxiliary file."
msgstr ""
"Ko kopirate prevod iz pomožne datoteke (<emphasis>sinhronizirane</"
"emphasis>), bodo vse nadaljnje spremembe te enote podvojene nazaj v pomožno "
"datoteko."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:372
#, no-c-format
msgid "Merging"
msgstr "Združevanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:373
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"One use of <guilabel>Sync Mode</guilabel> is reviewing changes made by (new) "
"contributors, when you cannot be sure of the quality of the work done."
msgstr ""
"Ena uporaba <guilabel>Načina sinhronizacije</guilabel> je pregledovanje "
"sprememb, ki so jih naredili (novi) sodelavci, ko niste prepričani o "
"kakovosti opravljenega dela."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:377
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Open a base file, then drop its changed version into the <guilabel>Primary "
"Sync</guilabel> view, followed by <keycombo>&Alt;<keycap>Down</keycap></"
"keycombo> or <keycombo>&Alt; <keycap>Up</keycap></keycombo> (remember that "
"shortcuts may be modified in a usual way for all &kde; applications) to "
"navigate through entries that are different."
msgstr ""
"Odprite osnovno datoteko, nato spustite njeno spremenjeno različico v pogled "
"<guilabel>Primarna sinhronizacija</guilabel>, čemur sledi <keycombo>&Alt;"
"<keycap>Dol</keycap></keycombo> ali <keycombo>&Alt; <keycap>Gor</keycap></"
"keycombo> (ne pozabite, da lahko bližnjice spremenite na običajen način za "
"vse programe &kde;) za krmarjenje med vnosi, ki so drugačni."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:384
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>&lokalize; used for merging changes in translation</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>&lokalize; uporabljen za združevanje sprememb v prevodu</"
"screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:390
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&lokalize; used for merging changes in translation</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>&lokalize; uporabljen za združevanje sprememb v prevodu</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:398
#, no-c-format
msgid "Replication"
msgstr "Replikacija"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:399
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Sync Mode</guilabel> may also be used to make changes to "
"translation for two branches simultaneously. Set <guilabel>Branch folder</"
"guilabel> path in your project options to the path that corresponds to base "
"folder of the branch, and <guilabel>Secondary Sync</guilabel> view will "
"automatically open files from branch. Then, each time you make changes in "
"files of your main branch, they will automatically be replicated to the "
"branch (of course, if it contains the same English string)."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Način sinhronizacije</guilabel> lahko uporabite tudi za "
"spreminjanje prevoda za dve veji hkrati. Nastavite pot <guilabel>Mapa veje</"
"guilabel> v možnostih vašega projekta na pot, ki ustreza osnovni mapi veje, "
"in pogled <guilabel>Sekundarne sinhronizacije</guilabel> bo samodejno odprl "
"datoteke iz veje. Potem, vsakič, ko naredite spremembe v datotekah vaše "
"glavne veje, bodo te samodejno podvojene v vejo (seveda, če vsebuje isti "
"angleški niz)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:408
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For example, if you work on &kde; translation, you can checkout trunk to "
"<filename class=\"directory\">/home/xx/hacking/kde/trunk/l10n-kf5/YOUR_LANG</"
"filename> and branch to <filename class=\"directory\">/home/xx/hacking/kde/"
"branches/stable/l10n-kf5/YOUR_LANG</filename>. Create &lokalize; project: "
"<filename>/home/xx/hacking/kde/trunk/l10n-kf5/YOUR_LANG/project.lokalize</"
"filename> and set <filename class=\"directory\">BranchDir=../../../branches/"
"stable/l10n-kf5/YOUR_LANG</filename>, then work via this project, and commit "
"changes in both trunk and branch folders."
msgstr ""
"Na primer, če delate na &kde; prevodu, lahko preverite deblo v <filename "
"class=\"directory\">/home/xx/hacking/kde/trunk/l10n-kf5/YOUR_LANG</filename> "
"in vejo v <filename class=\"directory\">/home/xx /hacking/kde/branches/"
"stable/l10n-kf5/VAŠ_JEZIK</filename>. Ustvari &lokalize; projekt: <filename>/"
"home/xx/hacking/kde/trunk/l10n-kf5/VAŠ_JEZIK/project.lokalize</filename> in "
"nastavite <filename class=\"directory\">BranchDir=../../../ branches/stable/"
"l10n-kf5/VAŠ_JEZIK</filename>, nato delajte prek tega projekta in potrdite "
"spremembe tako v glavnih mapah kot v mapah vej."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:419
#, no-c-format
msgid "Alternate Translations"
msgstr "Alternativni prevodi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:421
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each unit may have several <emphasis>alternate translations</emphasis> "
"associated with it. Such translations may appear during file update, when "
"the source string is slightly changed. In this case the old translation with "
"it's (old) source is moved to alternate translations list, so that they are "
"not lost."
msgstr ""
"Vsaka enota ima lahko povezanih več <emphasis>alternativnih prevodov</"
"emphasis>. Takšni prevodi se lahko pojavijo med posodobitvijo datoteke, ko "
"je izvorni niz nekoliko spremenjen. V tem primeru se stari prevod s svojim "
"(starim) virom premakne na seznam nadomestnih prevodov, tako da se ne "
"izgubijo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:426
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When translating software, usually gettext tools are used to prepare "
"translation files. When original text changes, gettext tools update "
"translation files and mark entries with changed original text as "
"<emphasis>fuzzy</emphasis> (or <emphasis>non-ready</emphasis> in other "
"terminology). They store previous original text so that translators could "
"see what changes exactly were made. &lokalize; simplifies the life of the "
"translator and highlights parts of the original text that were changed in "
"the <guilabel>Alternate Translations</guilabel> view."
msgstr ""
"Pri prevajanju programske opreme se običajno uporabljajo orodja gettext za "
"pripravo prevodnih datotek. Ko se izvirno besedilo spremeni, orodja gettext "
"posodobijo prevodne datoteke in označijo vnose s spremenjenim izvirnim "
"besedilom kot <emphasis>mehke</emphasis> (ali <emphasis>nepripravljene</"
"emphasis> v drugi terminologiji). Shranjujejo prejšnje izvirno besedilo, "
"tako da lahko prevajalci vidijo, katere spremembe so bile narejene. "
"&lokalize; poenostavi življenje prevajalca in poudari dele izvirnega "
"besedila, ki so bili spremenjeni v pogledu <guilabel>Nadomestni prevodi</"
"guilabel>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:434
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>&lokalize; highlighting parts of original text that were changed "
"since translation was last reviewed</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>&lokalize; poudarjanje delov izvirnega besedila, ki so bili "
"spremenjeni od zadnjega pregleda prevoda</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:440
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>&lokalize; highlighting parts of original text that were changed "
"since translation was last reviewed</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>&lokalize; poudarjanje delov izvirnega besedila, ki so bili "
"spremenjeni od zadnjega pregleda prevoda</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:451
#, no-c-format
msgid "External Tools"
msgstr "Zunanja orodja"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:454
#, no-c-format
msgid "Pology"
msgstr "Pology"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:456
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The interaction with <application>Pology</application> can be configured "
"using the page <guilabel>Pology</guilabel> of the configuration window which "
"can be opened by choosing the <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure &lokalize;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> main "
"menu item."
msgstr ""
"Interakcijo z <application>Pology-jem</application> lahko konfigurirate s "
"stranjo <guilabel>Pology</guilabel> konfiguracijskega okna, ki jo lahko "
"odprete tako, da izberete <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem> Konfiguriraj &lokalize;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
"element glavnega menija."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:459
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information, please refer to <ulink url=\"http://pology.nedohodnik."
"net/\">Pology homepage</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Za več informacij si oglejte <ulink url=\"http://pology.nedohodnik.net/"
"\">domačo stran Pology-ja</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:465
#, no-c-format
msgid "LanguageTool"
msgstr "LanguageTool"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:467
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<application>LanguageTool</application> offers spell and grammar checking of "
"your translation units."
msgstr ""
"<application>LanguageTool</application> ponuja preverjanje črkovanja in "
"slovnice vaših prevajalskih enot."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:470
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can configure your custom <application>LanguageTool</application> server "
"using the page <guilabel>LanguageTool</guilabel> of the configuration window "
"which can be opened by choosing the <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure &lokalize;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> main "
"menu item."
msgstr ""
"Strežnik <application>LanguageTool</application> po meri lahko konfigurirate "
"s stranjo <guilabel>LanguageTool</guilabel> konfiguracijskega okna, ki ga "
"lahko odprete tako, da izberete <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem> Konfiguriraj &lokalize;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
"element glavnega menija."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:473
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To utilize <application>LanguageTool</application> checking capabilities use "
"the <menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Check this unit using "
"LanguageTool</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item or use <keycombo>&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>J</keycap></keycombo> shortcut."
msgstr ""
"Za uporabo zmožnosti preverjanja <application>LanguageTool</application> "
"uporabite menijski element <menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Preveri to enoto z uporabo LanguageTool</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> ali uporabite <keycombo>&Ctrl; <keycap>J</keycap></keycombo> "
"bližnjico."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:476
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information, please refer to <ulink url=\"https://languagetool.org/"
"\">LanguageTool homepage</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Za več informacij si oglejte <ulink url=\"https://languagetool.org/\">domačo "
"stran LanguageTool-a</ulink>."

